# PHP / tests

## Adding features

- Mirror `src/` under `tests/TestCase/` (`*Test.php`).
- FileManager tests: isolated dir in `TMP`, restore `Configure` in `tearDown`, use `Laminas\Diactoros\UploadedFile` for uploads.
- Helper tests: `new View()` + load `BootstrapUI.Html` if output uses icons.

## FormHelper

- Custom types via `control()`: `image` ‚Üí element `Brammo/Admin.Form/image`; `html` ‚Üí loads `Form/editor` once, adds class `editor`.
- `imageControl` uses `$this->context()->val($fieldName)` ‚Äî tests need `Form->create($entity)` with valid entity context, not reflection on removed helpers.

## Do not

- Reference private methods removed from production code in tests.
- Use `in_array` without strict comparison for extension/MIME checks (use `in_array(..., true)`).
- Commit without running PHPUnit when touching `src/` or `tests/`.
